[FILE:423:descriptions/desc.single]
gert: Simple Git Client for R

Simple git client for R based on 'libgit2' &lt;<a
href="https://libgit2.org">https://libgit2.org</a>&gt; with support for SSH
and HTTPS remotes. All functions in 'gert' use basic R data types (such as
vectors and data-frames) for their arguments and return values. User
credentials are shared with command line 'git' through the git-credential
store and ssh keys stored on disk or ssh-agent.


